1
00:00:15,630 --> 00:00:19,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="78">HEAVENWARD</font>

2
00:00:17,130 --> 00:00:18,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Heavenward!</font>

3
00:00:20,330 --> 00:00:21,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yuuki...</font>

4
00:00:22,290 --> 00:00:25,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You just keep getting stronger, don't you?</font>

5
00:00:31,500 --> 00:00:33,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Now, let's put an end to this!</font>

6
00:00:33,960 --> 00:00:36,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Miss Mira... I'm on my way to save you!</font>

7
00:00:51,580 --> 00:00:56,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">My heart sunk and I no longer feel hope for the future</font>

8
00:00:56,500 --> 00:01:01,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">It felt like time froze and now it's all over</font>

9
00:01:01,670 --> 00:01:04,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Brooding and silent</font>

10
00:01:04,040 --> 00:01:07,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">The umbrella of my heart began to open</font>

11
00:01:07,710 --> 00:01:11,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Still, I kept my chin up and went on</font>

12
00:01:11,880 --> 00:01:15,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">I won't ask you to comfort me</font>

13
00:01:16,960 --> 00:01:20,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">I want to grow strong and focus on what's ahead</font>

14
00:01:20,830 --> 00:01:27,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">But weakness crushes me</font>

15
00:01:28,670 --> 00:01:33,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Meeting you is what filled my world with light</font>

16
00:01:33,670 --> 00:01:38,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">I didn't have an ounce of hope, and yet I could laugh</font>

17
00:01:38,540 --> 00:01:43,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Ordinary conversations always brought me a smile</font>

18
00:01:43,330 --> 00:01:47,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">I won't say thanks 'cause you'll blush and laugh</font>

19
00:01:47,040 --> 00:01:48,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">But I'm thinking it</font>

20
00:01:48,580 --> 00:01:52,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Can I move forward from here?</font>

21
00:01:52,630 --> 00:01:53,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">O light, come to me</font>

22
00:02:09,500 --> 00:02:11,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="60">Slave: Heaven</font>

23
00:02:09,500 --> 00:02:11,960
<font size="40"><b>{\an7}Episode 11</b></font>

24
00:02:30,830 --> 00:02:32,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Your trump card, huh?</font>

25
00:02:32,630 --> 00:02:33,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Fun!</font>

26
00:02:37,290 --> 00:02:39,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Now it's our turn!</font>

27
00:02:39,040 --> 00:02:40,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">On it!</font>

28
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:41,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Slave Support Fist!</font>

29
00:02:44,290 --> 00:02:46,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Predictable.</font>

30
00:02:53,880 --> 00:02:55,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Chains? Big deal!</font>

31
00:02:59,920 --> 00:03:01,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Above us!</font>

32
00:03:01,750 --> 00:03:03,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That's what happens
when you get caught in them?</font>

33
00:03:04,130 --> 00:03:06,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">They're no ordinary chains then!</font>

34
00:03:23,880 --> 00:03:26,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Coco... Naon...</font>

35
00:03:26,880 --> 00:03:28,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I've got you!</font>

36
00:03:29,080 --> 00:03:30,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You're already done!</font>

37
00:03:30,920 --> 00:03:33,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Stay outta this!</font>

38
00:03:34,080 --> 00:03:35,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yuuki! Cover me!</font>

39
00:03:36,880 --> 00:03:37,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Big Sis!</font>

40
00:03:43,830 --> 00:03:46,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Mighty Blade Cross!</font>

41
00:04:02,040 --> 00:04:03,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Stopped it, huh?</font>

42
00:04:03,670 --> 00:04:04,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Still...</font>

43
00:04:05,540 --> 00:04:08,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">A god's wrath will always be felt.</font>

44
00:04:13,880 --> 00:04:15,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Seriously?</font>

45
00:04:15,330 --> 00:04:18,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's one attack after the next.
This is gettin' old!</font>

46
00:04:18,750 --> 00:04:20,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'll keep drawing them in!</font>

47
00:04:25,880 --> 00:04:27,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">In the name of the Azumas!</font>

48
00:04:28,290 --> 00:04:30,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We'll hold the line!</font>

49
00:04:32,830 --> 00:04:34,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Ame-no-Mitori!</font>

50
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:39,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Heavenward!</font>

51
00:04:38,170 --> 00:04:41,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="78">HEAVENWARD</font>

52
00:04:40,580 --> 00:04:41,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Heavenward...</font>

53
00:04:41,580 --> 00:04:45,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="78">HEAVENWARD</font>

54
00:04:41,580 --> 00:04:45,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="35">(TENSHIN)</font>

55
00:04:41,580 --> 00:04:45,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="78">HEAVENLY FLOWER</font>

56
00:04:41,580 --> 00:04:45,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="35">(TENKA)</font>

57
00:04:42,250 --> 00:04:45,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'll be sure to live up to his feelings.</font>

58
00:05:14,460 --> 00:05:16,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Peaks of clouds above</font>

59
00:05:16,210 --> 00:05:18,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">How many sink to lay bare</font>

60
00:05:18,380 --> 00:05:19,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The moonlit mountain?</font>

61
00:05:21,960 --> 00:05:24,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Free my mind of its limits...</font>

62
00:05:26,880 --> 00:05:29,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">My movements will be enhanced
for a limited time.</font>

63
00:05:29,540 --> 00:05:32,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The technique I developed
to deal with the Eight Thunder Gods.</font>

64
00:05:39,130 --> 00:05:41,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'll show you a powerful technique
of my own!</font>

65
00:05:42,040 --> 00:05:43,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Bear witness!</font>

66
00:05:43,880 --> 00:05:47,750
<font size="60"><b>{\an7}MILLIONFOLD</b></font>

67
00:05:43,880 --> 00:05:47,750
<font size="60"><b>{\an7}DIVINE</b></font>

68
00:05:43,880 --> 00:05:47,750
<font size="60"><b>{\an7}PUNISHMENTS</b></font>

69
00:05:45,080 --> 00:05:47,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">To my breathtaking majesty!</font>

70
00:05:48,750 --> 00:05:50,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">She's only cloning her arms!</font>

71
00:06:24,420 --> 00:06:29,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Tremble in terror before my
Millionfold Divine Punishments!</font>

72
00:06:30,380 --> 00:06:31,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Picture it...</font>

73
00:06:31,670 --> 00:06:33,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">See it in your mind!</font>

74
00:06:43,210 --> 00:06:45,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">They broke through a god's multi-attack?!</font>

75
00:06:45,420 --> 00:06:47,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But I was going for the kill!</font>

76
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:51,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">A superficial hit.</font>

77
00:06:51,630 --> 00:06:53,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'll push harder with the next one!</font>

78
00:06:55,210 --> 00:06:56,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">All right!</font>

79
00:06:56,920 --> 00:07:00,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">To be on the safe side, I'll send
my clones to deliver the final blow!</font>

80
00:07:01,170 --> 00:07:02,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Go!</font>

81
00:07:09,960 --> 00:07:11,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What's wrong?</font>

82
00:07:12,750 --> 00:07:14,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Get out there with them!</font>

83
00:07:29,130 --> 00:07:30,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Mira?!</font>

84
00:07:32,290 --> 00:07:33,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Your clones are slow...</font>

85
00:07:34,920 --> 00:07:37,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You haven't absorbed Mira completely.</font>

86
00:07:44,290 --> 00:07:45,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Knock it off!</font>

87
00:07:47,540 --> 00:07:48,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Let's do it, Yuuki!</font>

88
00:07:48,960 --> 00:07:49,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yes, ma'am!</font>

89
00:08:01,500 --> 00:08:02,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Damn you, Mira!</font>

90
00:08:02,880 --> 00:08:06,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">When I gently opened my eyes</font>

91
00:08:03,790 --> 00:08:06,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You'll be fully assimilated before long!</font>

92
00:08:07,790 --> 00:08:09,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I am beautiful!</font>

93
00:08:07,790 --> 00:08:11,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">I was shrouded in darkness</font>

94
00:08:10,960 --> 00:08:12,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I am a god!</font>

95
00:08:12,630 --> 00:08:17,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">One... then another... I bore the sorrow</font>

96
00:08:16,420 --> 00:08:17,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I pledge my body...</font>

97
00:08:17,880 --> 00:08:20,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Through falling tears</font>

98
00:08:18,710 --> 00:08:20,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">to Miss Kyouka!</font>

99
00:08:20,290 --> 00:08:23,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">And I vowed to hold onto hope</font>

100
00:08:26,460 --> 00:08:28,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yuuki vanished?</font>

101
00:08:30,710 --> 00:08:31,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">No...</font>

102
00:08:32,670 --> 00:08:36,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yuuki's inside that sword!</font>

103
00:08:33,460 --> 00:08:37,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">I always had this dream</font>

104
00:08:38,330 --> 00:08:42,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">One so very far out of reach</font>

105
00:08:43,290 --> 00:08:47,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">It has to come true, that what I wished</font>

106
00:08:48,580 --> 00:08:53,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">That was the moment you and I connected</font>

107
00:08:50,040 --> 00:08:53,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Accept your punishment from on high!</font>

108
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:55,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">"Always be positive"</font>

109
00:08:55,380 --> 00:08:58,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">"Always be true"</font>

110
00:08:58,290 --> 00:09:02,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">If I'm with you, everything will be okay</font>

111
00:09:02,750 --> 00:09:08,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">I will turn this world into a garden of light</font>

112
00:09:03,670 --> 00:09:05,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Sword of Subjugation!</font>

113
00:09:03,670 --> 00:09:05,710
<font size="53"><b>{\an7}SWORD OF</b></font>

114
00:09:03,670 --> 00:09:05,710
<font size="53"><b>{\an7}SUBJUGATION</b></font>

115
00:09:07,250 --> 00:09:08,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Wha-</font>

116
00:09:08,210 --> 00:09:15,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">I swear I'll do it, I'll lead us to the future</font>

117
00:09:15,540 --> 00:09:16,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This...</font>

118
00:09:17,580 --> 00:09:19,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">...launches me from inside her sword...</font>

119
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:22,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">...using one of my lethal strikes.</font>

120
00:09:23,540 --> 00:09:25,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It combines my Heavenward power...</font>

121
00:09:25,830 --> 00:09:27,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">...with my martial arts.</font>

122
00:09:30,540 --> 00:09:32,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Ultimate dual technique!</font>

123
00:09:57,830 --> 00:10:00,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">They're all alive!</font>

124
00:10:12,540 --> 00:10:15,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">If you resist or try to pull
a disappearing act...</font>

125
00:10:17,080 --> 00:10:18,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">you die.</font>

126
00:10:30,330 --> 00:10:31,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Is this her default form?</font>

127
00:10:35,210 --> 00:10:36,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Look out!</font>

128
00:10:36,880 --> 00:10:39,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">If you insist on assimilating me...</font>

129
00:10:50,750 --> 00:10:52,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">then it's time to bow down.</font>

130
00:11:10,330 --> 00:11:11,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Heavenward...</font>

131
00:11:13,040 --> 00:11:14,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You made the most of it.</font>

132
00:11:18,420 --> 00:11:20,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Thank you, Miss Kyouka!</font>

133
00:11:24,380 --> 00:11:27,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I forgot!
What about Big Sis and her friends?</font>

134
00:11:30,330 --> 00:11:32,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Let me handle this.</font>

135
00:11:37,290 --> 00:11:40,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Don't move! If you do, I'll shoot!</font>

136
00:11:54,710 --> 00:11:56,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">She retreated underground...</font>

137
00:11:57,670 --> 00:12:00,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Thank you, Miss Tenka!</font>

138
00:12:03,500 --> 00:12:05,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Looks like ya conquered a god!</font>

139
00:12:07,250 --> 00:12:10,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Heal up and relay news
of the enemy's defeat.</font>

140
00:12:10,210 --> 00:12:13,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm going to secure the perimeter
just in case.</font>

141
00:12:13,250 --> 00:12:15,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'll get on the report.</font>

142
00:12:15,710 --> 00:12:19,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Leave the healing to me!
I got plenty of energy left!</font>

143
00:12:22,210 --> 00:12:23,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That's right!</font>

144
00:12:23,420 --> 00:12:27,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">With Miss Tovera here,
we'll be back on our feet soon enough!</font>

145
00:12:33,580 --> 00:12:37,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh crap... I can finally breathe, but...</font>

146
00:12:37,630 --> 00:12:41,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I feel like... I'm gonna...</font>

147
00:12:58,210 --> 00:12:59,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hi.</font>

148
00:13:02,250 --> 00:13:03,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Kuusetsu!</font>

149
00:13:04,040 --> 00:13:07,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Don't panic. None of this is real.</font>

150
00:13:08,790 --> 00:13:13,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's your inner world.
A mind palace of sorts.</font>

151
00:13:30,170 --> 00:13:33,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">My... inner world?</font>

152
00:13:33,540 --> 00:13:39,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I lost my corporeal form, so I manifested
where traces of my energy remained.</font>

153
00:13:39,250 --> 00:13:40,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Energy?</font>

154
00:13:40,330 --> 00:13:43,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You drank highly concentrated
divine nectar, remember?</font>

155
00:13:46,790 --> 00:13:48,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh, that...</font>

156
00:13:49,040 --> 00:13:52,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The thing about gods is,
they don't just vanish into thin air.</font>

157
00:13:53,540 --> 00:13:56,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That said, my corporeal form is gone.</font>

158
00:13:56,460 --> 00:14:01,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's impossible for me to affect
the ouside world, much less fight.</font>

159
00:14:06,420 --> 00:14:08,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You and I...</font>

160
00:14:08,420 --> 00:14:11,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">are left with no choice but to get along.</font>

161
00:14:18,040 --> 00:14:19,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You're about to wake up...</font>

162
00:14:20,420 --> 00:14:23,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Well, from now on, we can chat whenever.</font>

163
00:14:23,580 --> 00:14:28,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You should feel lucky having
a beautiful god living inside you.</font>

164
00:14:28,330 --> 00:14:31,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">L-lucky?</font>

165
00:14:40,290 --> 00:14:41,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Where am I?</font>

166
00:14:43,580 --> 00:14:46,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The 7th Squadron dorm in Mato, Mr. Yuuki!</font>

167
00:14:49,880 --> 00:14:52,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What? Was that whole thing a dream?!</font>

168
00:14:52,790 --> 00:14:54,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">H-huh? But...</font>

169
00:14:55,420 --> 00:14:58,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Calm down right now!
Senpai's orders!</font>

170
00:14:59,250 --> 00:15:00,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">O-okay.</font>

171
00:15:04,250 --> 00:15:08,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You lost consciousness after the battle
in Yokohama, Mr. Yuuki.</font>

172
00:15:08,580 --> 00:15:10,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You've been asleep for about two days.</font>

173
00:15:10,960 --> 00:15:13,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And they... brought me here?</font>

174
00:15:13,830 --> 00:15:15,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Your wounds have been healed.</font>

175
00:15:16,130 --> 00:15:18,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It seems you're perfectly healthy!</font>

176
00:15:18,960 --> 00:15:22,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The commander is at HQ with
Commander Kamiunten and the others</font>

177
00:15:22,170 --> 00:15:24,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">relaying what happened in Yokohama.</font>

178
00:15:24,540 --> 00:15:25,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">In that case...</font>

179
00:15:25,960 --> 00:15:28,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I should also get to work.</font>

180
00:15:29,580 --> 00:15:30,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">For today...</font>

181
00:15:31,920 --> 00:15:33,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">you should rest!</font>

182
00:15:37,000 --> 00:15:39,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Nei will handle the cooking.</font>

183
00:15:39,080 --> 00:15:41,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You should have a bath, too!</font>

184
00:15:41,500 --> 00:15:42,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Thanks.</font>

185
00:15:44,630 --> 00:15:48,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'll take Nei up on her offer
and freshen up first!</font>

186
00:15:51,880 --> 00:15:53,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I had a feeling you'd be awake.</font>

187
00:15:53,580 --> 00:15:56,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">My body started moving on its own.</font>

188
00:15:56,750 --> 00:15:58,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I forgot!</font>

189
00:15:58,000 --> 00:16:00,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">She hasn't given me my reward yet!</font>

190
00:16:00,460 --> 00:16:01,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">How are you feeling?</font>

191
00:16:01,750 --> 00:16:02,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Fit as a fiddle!</font>

192
00:16:03,130 --> 00:16:05,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Feelin' right as rain, myself!</font>

193
00:16:07,290 --> 00:16:09,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And they say you're the one who saved me!</font>

194
00:16:09,880 --> 00:16:11,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Thanks, kid!</font>

195
00:16:12,130 --> 00:16:13,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Everyone worked together.</font>

196
00:16:14,130 --> 00:16:15,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">He's right.</font>

197
00:16:15,540 --> 00:16:18,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">A victory earned
by all of the Demon Defense Force.</font>

198
00:16:20,670 --> 00:16:22,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Especially you, Mira.</font>

199
00:16:22,250 --> 00:16:24,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Fighting back even after she consumed you?</font>

200
00:16:24,750 --> 00:16:26,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Stubborn as ever.</font>

201
00:16:28,580 --> 00:16:33,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The thought of lettin' her absorb
all my power got me worked up.</font>

202
00:16:34,210 --> 00:16:36,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Perfect timing since we're all here!</font>

203
00:16:36,540 --> 00:16:38,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Lend me a hand with the debriefing.</font>

204
00:16:41,130 --> 00:16:44,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm sorry, but the debriefing has to wait.</font>

205
00:16:44,130 --> 00:16:46,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What?! How come?!</font>

206
00:16:48,170 --> 00:16:51,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">His reward is starting. Give us a minute.</font>

207
00:16:54,630 --> 00:16:56,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I intend to reward him, too.</font>

208
00:16:56,420 --> 00:16:57,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What for?!</font>

209
00:16:57,880 --> 00:17:00,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's like you said, Kyou-chin.</font>

210
00:17:00,000 --> 00:17:02,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This victory belongs
to the Demon Defense Force.</font>

211
00:17:03,420 --> 00:17:07,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">So those who can reward him should.</font>

212
00:17:05,210 --> 00:17:09,130
<font size="34" color="#ff80c0"><b>{\an7}Squeeze</b></font>

213
00:17:05,710 --> 00:17:09,130
<font size="34" color="#ff80c0"><b>{\an7}Squeeze</b></font>

214
00:17:06,380 --> 00:17:09,130
<font size="34" color="#ff80c0"><b>{\an7}Squee</b></font>

215
00:17:07,210 --> 00:17:09,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Is that the issue here?!</font>

216
00:17:07,330 --> 00:17:09,130
<font size="34" color="#ff80c0"><b>{\an7}eeeze</b></font>

217
00:17:10,170 --> 00:17:13,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">He did go out of his way
to rescue me himself...</font>

218
00:17:14,880 --> 00:17:17,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I-I'll help with the reward.</font>

219
00:17:17,130 --> 00:17:18,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Quit pressuring yourself.</font>

220
00:17:18,750 --> 00:17:19,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Wha-</font>

221
00:17:19,670 --> 00:17:22,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">From the looks of it,
we're taking a bath together.</font>

222
00:17:23,040 --> 00:17:26,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">A-a bath?!</font>

223
00:17:26,630 --> 00:17:29,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We don't even share a journal!</font>

224
00:17:26,630 --> 00:17:30,880
<font size="40" color="#ff80c0"><b>{\an7}Tremble</b></font>

225
00:17:26,630 --> 00:17:30,880
<font size="40" color="#ff80c0"><b>{\an7}Tremble</b></font>

226
00:17:29,170 --> 00:17:30,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">There's no way!</font>

227
00:17:32,250 --> 00:17:33,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And what the hell, Tenka?!</font>

228
00:17:33,920 --> 00:17:36,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Your body isn't moving on its own!</font>

229
00:17:36,920 --> 00:17:39,630
<font size="34"><b>{\an7}TURMOIL</b></font>

230
00:17:37,380 --> 00:17:39,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Why aren't you freaking out more?!</font>

231
00:17:58,830 --> 00:18:01,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I can't get undressed!
It's too embarrassing!</font>

232
00:18:02,000 --> 00:18:04,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And I was the one who suggested it!</font>

233
00:18:07,080 --> 00:18:11,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">B-being met with a sight like this...</font>

234
00:18:13,130 --> 00:18:15,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm so nervous, I'm paralyzed!</font>

235
00:18:16,130 --> 00:18:18,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Are you feeling dizzy?</font>

236
00:18:18,080 --> 00:18:20,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I think he's shy.</font>

237
00:18:27,460 --> 00:18:29,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Doing something like this
in a hot spring...</font>

238
00:18:29,960 --> 00:18:31,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Pervert.</font>

239
00:18:36,580 --> 00:18:38,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You did great out there.</font>

240
00:18:44,710 --> 00:18:46,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">U-um...</font>

241
00:18:46,170 --> 00:18:48,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Th-there's something you should know!</font>

242
00:18:48,830 --> 00:18:50,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What is it?</font>

243
00:18:55,580 --> 00:18:57,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">A god inside of Yuuki...</font>

244
00:18:57,830 --> 00:18:59,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Sounds harmless enough.</font>

245
00:18:59,880 --> 00:19:03,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's difficult to tell
whether it was just a dream.</font>

246
00:19:04,080 --> 00:19:05,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Right.</font>

247
00:19:05,130 --> 00:19:07,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I can't talk to her right now, either.</font>

248
00:19:08,960 --> 00:19:11,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'll be sure to keep a close eye on you.</font>

249
00:19:13,130 --> 00:19:14,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We'll see how it plays out.</font>

250
00:19:14,830 --> 00:19:16,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">From now on, report anything unusual.</font>

251
00:19:17,250 --> 00:19:19,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Y-yes, ma'am!</font>

252
00:19:24,210 --> 00:19:27,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">N-nope... Still can't do it!</font>

253
00:19:28,500 --> 00:19:31,080
<font size="40"><b>The Next Day</b></font>

254
00:19:33,830 --> 00:19:38,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">In anticipation of the
Eight Thunder Gods' next attack,</font>

255
00:19:38,250 --> 00:19:40,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Kyouka and Mira held a post-mortem
on the battle with Kuusetsu.</font>

256
00:19:41,330 --> 00:19:44,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">They focused on Mira's loss to Kuusetsu,</font>

257
00:19:44,670 --> 00:19:46,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">carefully reflecting
on what factors caused it.</font>

258
00:19:52,790 --> 00:19:55,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yup. In the end,
I shouldn't have come at her head-on.</font>

259
00:19:56,130 --> 00:20:00,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But it's because you were worn out
from saving the city-goers.</font>

260
00:20:00,040 --> 00:20:03,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">As a commander, I wish I could've
taken down a god, too.</font>

261
00:20:04,630 --> 00:20:08,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Everything turned out fine, I guess.
But I can't settle for less.</font>

262
00:20:09,330 --> 00:20:12,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">As talented as Miss Mira is,
she's extremely hard on herself.</font>

263
00:20:13,880 --> 00:20:14,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Kyouka.</font>

264
00:20:16,000 --> 00:20:18,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Lemme borrow the kid.</font>

265
00:20:28,790 --> 00:20:33,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Love beam!</font>

266
00:20:43,250 --> 00:20:46,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Wanna know and wanna do, wanna touch</font>

267
00:20:46,920 --> 00:20:52,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">These feelings pouring out of me just won't stop</font>

268
00:20:52,750 --> 00:20:59,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Sweet, so sweet, let me in with your body darling</font>

269
00:20:59,380 --> 00:21:02,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">I'll domesticate you, time for a reward</font>

270
00:21:02,960 --> 00:21:07,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">With the heat from skin on skin overlapping</font>

271
00:21:07,710 --> 00:21:10,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">It's fully charged</font>

272
00:21:10,710 --> 00:21:12,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Now ready to launch!</font>

273
00:21:12,960 --> 00:21:16,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Shoot from my hand now, love love beam</font>

274
00:21:16,080 --> 00:21:19,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Aim for your heart now, love love beam</font>

275
00:21:19,790 --> 00:21:23,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Bridging the gap between us</font>

276
00:21:23,630 --> 00:21:25,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">And firing from point blank</font>

277
00:21:25,750 --> 00:21:27,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Yay! Yay! Yay! Yay!</font>

278
00:21:27,250 --> 00:21:30,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">You won't escape my love love beam</font>

279
00:21:30,670 --> 00:21:34,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">To the ends of the Earth, love love beam</font>

280
00:21:34,290 --> 00:21:38,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Yeah, love is what changes the world</font>

281
00:21:38,040 --> 00:21:44,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Dye it all heart-colored, even the darkness</font>

282
00:21:52,330 --> 00:21:56,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This is the story of a dream
that Yuuki had!</font>

283
00:21:56,540 --> 00:21:59,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">High school?! What am I doing here?!</font>

284
00:22:08,500 --> 00:22:09,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hello?</font>

285
00:22:10,670 --> 00:22:12,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Quit zoning out
first thing in the morning.</font>

286
00:22:12,920 --> 00:22:14,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Uh, s-sorry!</font>

287
00:22:16,330 --> 00:22:18,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yo, underclassman!</font>

288
00:22:23,670 --> 00:22:25,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hey! Lessons are starting soon!</font>

289
00:22:25,960 --> 00:22:27,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Get to the classroom!</font>

290
00:22:27,330 --> 00:22:30,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Everyone's a student now?!</font>

291
00:22:32,000 --> 00:22:36,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This is your world.
I can make things like this happen.</font>

292
00:22:36,210 --> 00:22:37,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">A god meddling in my head?!</font>

293
00:22:37,880 --> 00:22:39,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Combing through your memories...</font>

294
00:22:39,880 --> 00:22:43,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You didn't have a mate in school, did you?</font>

295
00:22:44,920 --> 00:22:46,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'll be your mate.</font>

296
00:22:53,000 --> 00:22:55,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We'll pick up where we left off!</font>

297
00:23:00,290 --> 00:23:01,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Wh-what's going on?</font>

298
00:23:01,920 --> 00:23:04,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">My body's moving on its own again!</font>

299
00:23:05,580 --> 00:23:06,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Play it cool!</font>

300
00:23:06,920 --> 00:23:09,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">There's a ton of questions
you need to ask!</font>

301
00:23:11,380 --> 00:23:14,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I have to turn this around before-</font>

302
00:23:21,790 --> 00:23:23,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Ah, he escaped!</font>

303
00:23:23,420 --> 00:23:25,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yuuki cuts class.</font>

304
00:23:26,380 --> 00:23:30,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="69">Gods Assemble</font>

305
00:23:26,380 --> 00:23:30,040
<font size="40"><b>Episode 12</b></font>

306
00:23:26,830 --> 00:23:29,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Next time, Episode 12: "Gods Assemble"!</font>

307
00:23:30,250 --> 00:23:31,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Here's today's bonus!</font>

308
00:23:31,920 --> 00:23:34,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Welcome to Slave High School!</font>

309
00:23:34,170 --> 00:23:36,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh, you don't have a mate?</font>

310
00:23:36,500 --> 00:23:37,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Well, in that case...</font>

311
00:23:37,670 --> 00:23:40,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'll be your mate.</font>

